paragraphs.text:
val myDF = spark.sql("""
SELECT sc.id, qh.command_id, qh.submit_time, qh.end_time,  (end_time - submit_time)  as jobTimeInSecs, case when qh.status_code = 0 then 'success'
     else 'error'
     end AS status, 
qh.status_code,
sc.cmdline, sc.arguments, sc.language, qh.account_id, qh.tag, tc.cluster_id, tc.custom_spark_config,
tc.master_type,
tc.slave_type, 
tc.initial_nodes,
tc.max_nodes,
tc.is_spot, 
tc.spark_version,
tc.uses_ebs,
tc.custom_hadoop_config,
tc.cluster_inst_id, 
tc.cluster_start_at, 
tc.cluster_down_at 
FROM rstore.spark_commands sc, rstore.query_hists qh
LEFT JOIN 
(
 SELECT ct.tag, ct.account_id, ct.cluster_id, ct.enabled_at as tag_enabled_at, ct.disabled_at as tag_disabled_at, 
        cc.created_at as config_created_at, cc.updated_at as config_updated_at, cc.is_latest as config_is_latest,
        cc.custom_spark_config,
        cc.hadoop_master_type as master_type,
        cc.hadoop_slave_type as slave_type,
        cc.hadoop_initial_nodes as initial_nodes,
        cc.hadoop_max_nodes as max_nodes,
        case when cc.hadoop_slave_request_type = 'spot' then true 
        else false 
        end as is_spot,
        cc.spark_version,
        case when cc.ebs_volume_count > 0 then true 
        else false
        end as uses_ebs,
        cc.custom_hadoop_config,
        ci.id as cluster_inst_id,
        ci.start_at as cluster_start_at,
        ci.down_at as cluster_down_at
 FROM   rstore.cluster_tags ct, rstore.cluster_configs cc, rstore.cluster_insts ci
 WHERE  ct.cluster_id = cc.cluster_id
 AND    cc.cluster_id = ci.cluster_id
 AND    cc.id = ci.cluster_config_id 
) tc
ON     UPPER(TRIM(qh.tag)) = UPPER(TRIM(tc.tag))
AND    tc.account_id = qh.account_id
AND    tc.tag_enabled_at < qh.created_at 
AND    (tc.tag_disabled_at > qh.created_at OR tc.tag_disabled_at IS NULL)
AND    tc.config_created_at < qh.created_at 
AND    (tc.config_updated_at > qh.created_at OR tc.config_is_latest=true)
AND    tc.cluster_start_at < qh.created_at 
AND    tc.cluster_down_at > qh.updated_at 
WHERE  qh.command_type="SparkCommand"

paragraphs.title: Concurrent commands running
paragraphs.text:
val commandsDF = spark.sql("""select (hour(from_unixtime(submit_time)) * 60 + minute(from_unixtime(submit_time))) as queryStart, 
         CAST ((jobTimeInSecs/60) as INT) as minutes
from new_spark_commands
where cluster_id=45770
and cluster_inst_id = 1616598 
""")
val deflatedDF = commandsDF.flatMap( x => {
    val startMinute = x.getInt(0)
    val list = new Array[(Int, Int)](x.getInt(1))
    for (i <- 0 to x.getInt(1)-1) {
        list(i) = (startMinute+i, 1)
    }
    list.toSeq
}) 
deflatedDF.createOrReplaceTempView("deflated_commands")

select ab.memoryPerCore, ab.status, count(*)

 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  3000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  4000 then 'a4000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  4000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  5000 then 'a5000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  5000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  6000 then 'a6000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  6000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  7000 then 'a7000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  7000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  8000 then 'a8000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  8000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  9000 then 'a9000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  9000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  10000 then 'b10000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  10000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  11000 then 'b11000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  11000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  12000 then 'b12000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  12000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  13000 then 'b13000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  13000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  14000 then 'b14000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  14000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  15000 then 'b15000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  15000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  16000 then 'b16000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  16000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  17000 then 'b17000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  17000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  18000 then 'b18000'
 when (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores >=  18000 AND  (executorMemoryMB+executorOverheadMB)/executorCores <  19000 then 'b19000'

and slave_type is NOT NULL
and cluster_id = 45770

group by memoryPerCore, status
order by memoryPerCore

paragraphs.title: Number of commands with given memory wastage

%sql 

select sub.wastage, count(*) as commandCount
from 
(select id, case 
when memoryWastagePercent < 10 THEN "10"
when memoryWastagePercent >=10 AND memoryWastagePercent < 20 THEN "20"
when memoryWastagePercent >=20 AND memoryWastagePercent < 30 THEN "30"
when memoryWastagePercent >=30 AND memoryWastagePercent < 40 THEN "40"
when memoryWastagePercent >=40 AND memoryWastagePercent < 50 THEN "50"
when memoryWastagePercent >=40 AND memoryWastagePercent < 50 THEN "50"
else "50+"
end as wastage
from new_spark_commands
where executorMemoryMB > 0
and slave_type is NOT NULL
and cluster_id=45770 
--and account_id = 3321
) sub 
group by sub.wastage
order by sub.wastage
